text:

text:
Into an #abyss I fall & welcome it
Bliss,after a long,long week
Sweet dreams to salve the wounds mind accrues
Trying to navigate
Traffic & din of voices; lives overlapping
The crush of a commuter train
The warm air,underground
Spreading,a contagion of lethargic despair

Title: Abyss, The
description: Is the dream the inspiration or the inspiration the dream? Do your lyrics come from your heart or are they hidden in your soul?
text:
#vssnature

I stare
into the #abyss
wondering
if this truly is
a entry into hell
or just the last kiss
of a lost star
searching for home

Count 125
